      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Bird Wyvern Jamboree",
        "Client": "Lance-Wielding Knight",
        "Description": "We\u0027ve gotten word of a merchant\r\nlost deep in the Shrine Ruins.\r\nWe have a bead on their location,\r\nbut we\u0027ve also gotten word of an\r\nAknosom and a Kulu-Ya-Ku there.\r\nHunt down both, and we\u0027ll rescue\r\nthe merchant.",
